  "instructions": [
    "Heat chocolate, milk and cumin in a saucepan until melted.",
    "Stir in vanilla extract. Remove from heat.",
    "Add oats and salt to a mixing bowl. Gradually pour almond milk over the top while continuously stirring with a wooden spoon or spatula.",
    "Mix well until smooth, then let it cool slightly.",
    "Pour mixture into a lined baking dish, smoothing the top with a spatula.",
    "Bake at 180°C (350°F) for 25 minutes or until firm.",
    "Allow to cool completely before slicing and serving."
